<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Hambúrguer com Queijo e Bacon</title>

<style>

body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background:#f4f4f4;
    margin:0;
}

header{
    background:#c0392b;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
    text-align:center;
}

.container{
    max-width:900px;
    margin:40px auto;
    background:white;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    overflow:hidden;
}

.image{
    width:100%;
    height:350px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.content{
    padding:25px;
}

h1{
    margin-top:0;
}

.price{
    font-size:24px;
    color:#27ae60;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.ingredients{
    margin-top:20px;
}

.ingredients li{
    margin:6px 0;
}

button{
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:12px 20px;
    border:none;
    background:#e67e22;
    color:white;
    font-size:16px;
    border-radius:6px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

button:hover{
    background:#d35400;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>🍔 Hambúrguer com Queijo e Bacon</h1>
</header>

<div class="container">

<img class="image"
src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550547660-d9450f859349"
alt="Hamburguer com queijo e bacon">

<div class="content">

<h2>Descrição</h2>
<p>
Um delicioso hambúrguer artesanal com carne suculenta,
queijo cheddar derretido e bacon crocante,
servido em pão macio com molho especial da casa.
</p>

<h2>Ingredientes</h2>
<ul class="ingredients">
<li>Pão brioche</li>
<li>Carne bovina 180g</li>
<li>Queijo cheddar</li>
<li>Bacon crocante</li>
<li>Alface</li>
<li>Tomate</li>
<li>Molho especial</li>
</ul>

<p class="price">R$ 24,90</p>

<button>Adicionar ao pedido</button>

</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>